    <readme><![CDATA[(( XSLTsearch 2.8.1 is for use with Umbraco 4.1's new xml schema. Use XSLTsearch 2.8 with Umbraco 3.x, 4.0, or 4.1 with the legacy xml schema enabled. ))
    
XSLTsearch is the ideal search solution for umbraco web sites with up to a few thousand pages. It is fast, completely self-contained in one xslt file, and extremely configurable.

With XSLTsearch you can search for words, phrases, portions of words, and portions of phrases in all document properties and attributes, including your custom properties. Search results are automatically sorted by relevance with search terms highlighted in the results.

XSLTsearch installs in all umbraco sites, with or without Runway installed.]]></readme>
